text: The Cronulla-Sutherland Sharks are an Australian professional rugby league team. The team is based in Cronulla, southern Sydney, New South Wales. They were founded in 1963. They currently play in the National Rugby League competition. They have won one premiership in 2016 against the Melbourne Storm. ==Other websites== * Category:National Rugby League Category:Sports clubs and teams in Sydney Category:1963 establishments Category:1960s establishments in Australia
